des:
The official skill of The General Consensus, Hamilton-Wenham Regional High School’s student-run newspaper. Our mission is to inform our community about what is going on in and out of school, as well as to give students a voice in issues that affect their lives.
This skill was developed by Sarah McMahon for the House of High Fives, LLC.
